Syntax: pummel <target>

Delivers a rapid series of unarmed blows using the Pugilist attack system.
Pummel represents the core repeated-strike technique of the Pugilist class,
emphasizing quick successive hits over single powerful blows.

Pummel is available to Pugilist-class characters and their remort
descendants (Monk, Brawler, Martial Artist).

Requirements:
  - Must be in combat or initiates combat on the target.
  - Target must be present in the room.
  - Must have the skill learned.

See also: shelp pummel punch aurabolt palmstrike spinfist
